ight.";i:21;s:30:"23 - 24 Bar Stool Seat Height.";i:22;s:26:"29 30 Dining Table Height.";i:23;s:27:"29 30 Counter Table Height.";i:24;s:27:"36 Bar or Pub Table Height.";i:25;s:21:"42 There you have it.";i:26;s:105:"15 rows The general rule for tables in early care and education classrooms is the space between the seat.";i:27;s:96:"Do you need help deciding on the height of table you require and the corresponding chair height.";i:28;s:198:"This simple to use height guide illustrates the recommended heights for both tabling and seating in accordance with the European standard EN1729 Part 1 for Dimensional fit used for school furniture.";i:29;s:103:"However standard chair height non-adjustable ones are about 18-inches measured from the floor the seat.";i:30;s:177:"When it comes to finding the perfect and comfortable ergonomic chair youll want to make sure that your chair can be adjusted to your comfort more than just adjusting its height.";i:31;s:106:"Some chairs will give you the ability to tilt adjust its armrest and also adjust the seat position itself.";i:32;s:111:"Ideally standard tables will have chairs that are 18 to 23 inches tall with a table thats 28 to 30 inches tall.";i:33;s:167:"However taller ones demand taller chairs or even stools counters demand chairs that are around 26 inches tall while bar stools need to be at least 28 inches in height.";i:34;s:40:"Standard chair and standard desk height.";i:35;s:49:"The average desk height is 29 inches tall approx.";i:36;s:106:"Unfortunately that height is suitable for only a small part of the population - people around 6 feet tall.";i:37;s:114:"Theres no standard desk height for stand up tables but you can expect them to be around 38-42 97-107 cm in height.";i:38;s:64:"Pub tables also called bar tables measure around 42 inches tall.";i:39;s:135:"When selecting a chair to coordinate with a pub table the seat height of the chair should measure 10 to 12 inches less than the height.";i:40;s:64:"These tables are someti