ywhere from 16 to 19 inches from the floor to the top of the seat.";i:59;s:100:"As you can see in the above section the seat heights for all of our chairs fall within these ranges.";i:60;s:56:"Again just look for a gap of 9 to 13 inches between the.";i:61;s:93:"Leave seven inches between the chair arm height and the table apron bottom edge of the table.";i:62;s:37:"Chairs can be built in three heights.";i:63;s:45:"Standard counter and bar or gathering height.";i:64;s:86:"Standard height chairs are 18- 23 tall and are available in a wide variety of designs.";i:65;s:91:"Chair height also varies based on the recommended age range of the children who may use it.";i:66;s:56:"There is no standard for chair back height but the seat.";}}